GENWI is seeking a savvy wordsmith and all around marketing superstar to join our marketing team. The ideal candidate will be a writer first but be prepared to help with other marketing activities in an exciting start-&shy;‐up environment.<br />
Candidates must have a knack and love for writing, an appreciation of the mobile industry, and will be expected to sustain and develop the company&#39;s voice across all content marketing materials.<br />
In addition, candidates should have some experience in &ndash; or a desire to learn &ndash; marketing operations to help with the day-&shy;‐to-&shy;‐day running of various aspects of the companies marketing programs.</p>
<p>
The ideal candidate will have:<br />
&bull; A minimum of 2-&shy;‐3 years of content creation and marketing or sales administrative experience<br />
&bull; An excellent attention to detail<br />
&bull; A fresh creative approach<br />
&bull; A passion and strong understanding of the mobile publishing industry and<br />
our business&#39; mission<br />
&bull; Exceptional writing and editorial skills, as well as the ability to adopt the<br />
