&bull; Managing the content marketing schedule &ndash; including having the initiative to find interesting and relevant content ideas<br />
&bull; Writing various types of articles on a wide range of topics<br />
&bull; Providing feedback to other contributors and editing other writers&rsquo; content.<br />
